---
title: Char Siu Double Pork & Sticky Eggplant with Ginger Rice & Peanuts
description: What’s an instant way to bring bold, international flavours to two types of pork? Add this sweet 'n' salty char siu paste to tender
pork loin steaks. Teamed with sticky braised eggplant and pork mince, plus an aromatic garlic rice, this meal will make your
tastebuds sing!
